{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-053__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-001", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-053", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-053__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "老子 53.1", "sort_key": "053.001", "text_original": "使我介然有知，行於大道，唯施是畏。", "text_normalized": "使我介然有知，行於大道，唯施是畏。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-053__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-002", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-053", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-053__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "老子 53.2", "sort_key": "053.002", "text_original": "大道甚夷，而民好徑。", "text_normalized": "大道甚夷，而民好徑。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-053__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-003", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-053", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-053__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "老子 53.3", "sort_key": "053.003", "text_original": "朝甚除，", "text_normalized": "朝甚除，", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-053__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-004", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-053", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-053__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "老子 53.4", "sort_key": "053.004", "text_original": "田甚蕪，倉甚虛；", "text_normalized": "田甚蕪，倉甚虛；", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-053__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-005", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-053", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-053__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "老子 53.5", "sort_key": "053.005", "text_original": "服文綵，帶利劍，厭飲食，財貨有餘；是為盜夸。非道也哉！", "text_normalized": "服文綵，帶利劍，厭飲食，財貨有餘；是為盜夸。非道也哉！", "notes": ""}
